                        <li id="comment-6411639332" class="c-article-comments-list__item">
                            
                                <p class="c-article-comments-list__submitted"><span class="c-article-comments-list__author">PD Cornelius Werner, MD</span> <time datetime="2024-03-12T12:01:40Z" class="c-article-comments-list__date">12 March 2024, 12:01</time></p>
                            
                            <p>This will be remembered as the paper that started it all: Equipping LLMs with the capabilities of using visual information directly from sensors, retrieving information from a vast data repository (i.e., memory) and programming a mechanical effector in order to achieve results in the real world. Awesome.</p>
